WEBVTT

00:00:00.988 --> 00:00:03.983
Today I have just one request.

00:00:03.983 --> 00:00:07.373
Please don't tell me I'm normal.

00:00:07.373 --> 00:00:11.749
Now I'd like to introduce you to my brothers.

00:00:11.749 --> 00:00:14.015
Remi is 22,

00:00:14.015 --> 00:00:16.979
tall and very handsome.

00:00:16.979 --> 00:00:20.907
He's speechless, but he communicates joy

00:00:20.907 --> 00:00:25.190
in a way that some of the best orators cannot.

00:00:25.190 --> 00:00:27.833
Remi knows what love is.

00:00:27.833 --> 00:00:32.215
He shares it unconditionally and he shares it regardless.